  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You heard the other one breaking into the house and going upstairs to the third floor where we lived, supposed to have lived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The neighbors told them that we had been picked up already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they didn't really-- fortunately, didn't start searching all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they-- the [INAUDIBLE] were all-- you know, they didn't keep any sort of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but then what happened is after they left, they put out a seal that that house, you know, people had gone and then the collaborators could go in with one of the German high commands and take out whatever they felt was they could use.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after they had left, maybe hours later, or the next day, I don't remember, we went back up and there were all the seals.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to break to get into our own house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was, just then my parents really got hold of the underground and said, well, it's time to move.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was in a few days I was taken by the underground to my hiding place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did your parents prepare you for your being taken?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they just told me it was just for a small holiday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what they, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were going to go on holidays themselves, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they, they didn't know where I was going, or nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just that, you know, the underground was, you know, going to take care of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, saying goodbye and moving with the, the g-- the person who picked me up at the house down to the street car without the star because I was-- you know, you couldn't have that on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At the corner of the square was a laundry of-- you know, washing, for washing facilities.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
